{"root":{"data":{"id":"d50jaytbapz4","created":1729417402662,"text":"辛普森多样性指数"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jbvo4jym8","created":1729417474182,"text":"群落中种数越多，各种个体分配越均匀，指数越低，群落多样性越高，对均匀度和群落中优势的OTU更敏感。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jc2x7xq80","created":1729417489970,"text":"计算公式","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jc9w24pvk","created":1729417505137,"text":"D=1−∑(pi^2​)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jcpdeiigw","created":1729417538837,"text":"D 是辛普森多样性指数，表示群落的多样性程度，值的范围在0到1之间。\n值越接近1，表示多样性越高；值越接近0，表示多样性越低"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jcudjt5a8","created":1729417549730,"text":"(pi) 是群落中第i个物种的相对丰度，即该物种在群落中的比例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jny5340zk","created":1729418419931,"text":"∑(pi^2​)表示所有物种相对丰度的平方和"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d50jp0k8h0xs","created":1729418503565,"text":"例子"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jprj4skxs","created":1729418562272,"text":"样本1：均匀分布"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-pink-compat","version":"1.4.43"}